androidx.lifecycle

Interface LifecycleObserver

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DefaultLifecycleObserver, androidx.lifecycle.FullLifecycleObserver, GenericLifecycleObserver
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeGeneratedAdaptersObserver, SingleGeneratedAdapterObserver, ViewDataBinding.OnStartListener

    public interface LifecycleObserver
    Marks a class as a LifecycleObserver. It does not have any methods, instead, relies on OnLifecycleEvent annotated methods.

    See Also:
    Lifecycle - for samples and usage patterns.

Generated javadoc for the new package structure to make it clearer which packages are bundled with the Android operating system, and which are packaged with your app's APK. Going forward, the android.* package hierarchy will be reserved for Android packages that ship with the operating system; other packages will be issued in the new androidx.* package hiearchy.
